 \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"the quarterfinal\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1112}, {\"ngram\": \"the semifinal\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many fans are saying Phogat's disqualification was particularly heartbreaking given what she represents to women back home.\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1187, \"end\": 1193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many fans\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year, she led a group of fellow wrestlers in protesting the behavior of then-WFI president and lawmaker Brij Bhushan Sharan Singh.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a group\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"fellow wrestlers\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1336}, {\"ngram\": \"the behavior\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1363}, {\"ngram\": \"then-WFI president\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"lawmaker Brij Bhushan Sharan Singh\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In aJanuary 2023 letter, the group accused Singh of sexual harassment against several young female wrestlers.\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1535, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"aJanuary 2023 letter\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"the group\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual harassment\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"several young female wrestlers\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1534}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also alleged that, after Phogat missed out on a medal at the Tokyo Olympics, Singh \\\"mentally harassed and tortured\\\" her, driving the wrestler to the point of almost contemplating suicide.\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1564, \"end\": 1570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1614}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrestler\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1693}, {\"ngram\": \"suicide\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The group led by Phogat demanded an investigation and called for Singh to be axed, and for the WFI to be dissolved.Allegationsagainst Singh have included groping and inappropriate physical contact.\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1745, \"end\": 1751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The group\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1737}, {\"ngram\": \"an investigation\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1798}, {\"ngram\": \"the WFI\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"Allegationsagainst Singh\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"groping\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1889}, {\"ngram\": \"inappropriate physical contact\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He waschargedwith assault, stalking and sexual harassment in June of last year and thetrialis currently underway.\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 2039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"assault\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1951}, {\"ngram\": \"stalking and sexual harassment\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1983}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 1991}, {\"ngram\": \"last year\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2004}, {\"ngram\": \"thetrialis\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2019}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He hasdenied the allegationson multiple occasions.\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2090, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the allegationson multiple occasions\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We as senior wrestlers who fight for the country only want to ensure a safe and secure place and environment for our young wrestlers especially female wrestlers,\\\" Phogat and several other athletes wrote in the letter to the Indian Olympic Association.\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2317, \"end\": 2343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Indian Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Olympic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"senior wrestlers\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"a safe and secure place\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2185}, {\"ngram\": \"environment\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"our young wrestlers\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2225}, {\"ngram\": \"especially female wrestlers\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2253}, {\"ngram\": \"several other athletes\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2289}, {\"ngram\": \"the letter\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They do not deserve to be in an environment of intimidation.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2406, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an environment\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2389}, {\"ngram\": \"intimidation\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will not budge until the WFI President is sacked.\\\"\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the WFI President\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the course of several months, the wrestlers also lodged police complaints and launched marches and other forms of resistance.\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2477}, {\"ngram\": \"several months\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrestlers\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2510}, {\"ngram\": \"police complaints\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"marches\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"other forms\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2577}, {\"ngram\": \"resistance\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last May, Phogat and other protesters wereviolently draggedand detained by riot police, accused of disturbing the peace after they attempted to march toward the Parliament building.\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2603, \"end\": 2609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}, {\"begin\": 2754, \"end\": 2764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliament_of_India\", \"score\": 0.9999924654309412, \"rank\": 6.9861792358528295e-06, \"text\": \"Parliament\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliament_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Parliament_of_India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Last May\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2601}, {\"ngram\": \"wereviolently draggedand\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2655}, {\"ngram\": \"riot police\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2679}, {\"ngram\": \"the peace\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also slept on the streets of New Delhi for40 daysbefore Singh was charged.\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2809, \"end\": 2818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"score\": 0.99704964802047, \"rank\": 0.002959082313804939, \"text\": \"New Delhi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2805}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today we can stand without fear, our head held high, look him in the eye, the man we were afraid of for so many years,\\\" Phogat wrote in theIndian Express.\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 3011, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fear\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2888}, {\"ngram\": \"our head\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 2898}, {\"ngram\": \"the eye\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2929}, {\"ngram\": \"the man\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2938}, {\"ngram\": \"so many years\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 2974}, {\"ngram\": \"Phogat\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 2983}, {\"ngram\": \"theIndian Express\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Brij Bhushan has got the message that we are not going anywhere until women wrestlers get justice.\\\"\", \"from\": 3012, \"to\": 3112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brij Bhushan\", \"from\": 3013, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"the message\", \"from\": 3034, \"to\": 3045}, {\"ngram\": \"women wrestlers\", \"from\": 3083, \"to\": 3098}, {\"ngram\": \"justice\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After Phogat's disqualification, India'sopposition leadersinterrupted Parliament to demand that Prime Minister Narendra Modi speak out against it.\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\